title: Lunchbox Had To Call 9-1-1 For Something He Saw on Road + Bobby’s Mailbag: Listener Advice on Dating 17-year old Intern + Iconic Sounds Game
itunes:title: Lunchbox Had To Call 9-1-1 For Something He Saw on Road + Bobby’s Mailbag: Listener Advice on Dating 17-year old Intern + Iconic Sounds Game
description:
Lunchbox tells us a crazy story about how he was on the phone for 30 minutes with 9-11. A listener emailed the show on advice about if he could date a new 17 year old intern at his job…and he’s 22 by the way! Bobby and the crew play a game where they have to identify the iconic sound!
